item.title: First Post
item.description: Today I got this site up and running using Hugo. I’m mainly hoping to use it as a place to write about my experiences working on my projects, and to put info about those projects.

item.title: About
item.description: I’m a college computer science student who has just started working on real projects. My interests are AI, web development, and systems programming. Hopefully I’ll eventually get some projects related to all of those fields finished enough that I want to put them up here.

item.title: Slime Chan
item.description: Background SlimeChan was my first real attempt at building a web application. I started it back in late 2019, but after running into some difficulties with it early on I took a long break before coming back this summer and getting it into its current (mostly finished) state.
